    <item>
      <title>南非将中国视为其农产品的主要市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/south-africa-targets-china-as-key-market-for-its-farm-produce</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非新成立的十党联合政府计划增加对中国的农产品出口，这是其与中国建立更紧密联系、提振经济和应对 34% 失业率的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/south-africa-targets-china-as-key-market-for-its-farm-produce</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本各省要求预算达创纪录的 8110 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/japan-s-ministries-ask-for-record-811-billion-to-fund-spending-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本各省对2025年4月开始的年度预算要求创下了新纪录，因为该国正在努力增加社会保障和国防开支，同时控制巨额债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/japan-s-ministries-ask-for-record-811-billion-to-fund-spending-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:08:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>媒体称金正恩在洪水灾害后处决官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/kim-jong-un-executes-officials-after-deadly-floods-media-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据朝鲜电视台报道，7 月底，朝鲜北部地区发生严重洪灾，造成数千人死亡，随后朝鲜处决了多名政府官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/kim-jong-un-executes-officials-after-deadly-floods-media-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:08:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔资金困境使拜登团队的芯片战略陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/intel-s-money-woes-throw-biden-team-s-chip-strategy-into-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登-哈里斯政府大举押注英特尔公司引领美国芯片制造业复兴，但由于英特尔日益严重的财务困境，这一赌注陷入严重困境，这可能会对美国几十年来最雄心勃勃的产业政策造成严重挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/intel-s-money-woes-throw-biden-team-s-chip-strategy-into-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰大变动：西比哈或将成为下一任外交部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/sybiha-set-to-become-ukraine-s-next-foreign-minister-in-shakeup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据了解总统想法的人士透露，在泽连斯基改组政府之际，乌克兰外交官安德烈·西比哈 (Andrii Sybiha) 预计将取代德米特罗·库列巴 (Dmytro Kuleba) 担任外交部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/sybiha-set-to-become-ukraine-s-next-foreign-minister-in-shakeup</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 08:50:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑分两步降低抵押贷款利率以保护银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-weighs-cutting-mortgage-rates-in-two-steps-to-shield-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正考虑分两步降低高达 5.3 万亿美元的抵押贷款利率，以降低数百万家庭的借贷成本，同时缓解银行系统的利润紧缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-weighs-cutting-mortgage-rates-in-two-steps-to-shield-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 08:30:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及总统塞西访问土耳其，试图修复与埃尔多安的不和</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/egypt-s-el-sisi-visits-turkey-in-move-to-repair-erdogan-discord</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及总统阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西将于周三在安卡拉会见土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安，两国寻求修复近期紧张的关系，并在能源、国防和加沙战争方面开展更密切的合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/egypt-s-el-sisi-visits-turkey-in-move-to-repair-erdogan-discord</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 08:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>企业家对工党的资本利得税威胁发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/entrepreneurs-raise-the-alarm-over-labour-s-capital-gains-tax-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者和企业家警告称，如果工党政府在十月份的预算中提高资本利得税，英国将失去快速增长的初创企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/entrepreneurs-raise-the-alarm-over-labour-s-capital-gains-tax-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国服务业扩张放缓 显现经济疲软新迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-services-expansion-cools-in-new-sign-of-economic-weakness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项私人调查显示，中国服务业活动扩张低于预期，加剧了人们对经济健康状况的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-services-expansion-cools-in-new-sign-of-economic-weakness</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 01:51:19 GMT</pubDate>
